#Process:

Create a Kinesis Data Stream
Populate the Kinesis stream with mock data
Confirm data visibility in the Kinesis stream
Establish a Lambda function to retrieve data from Kinesis and store it in DynamoDB, using the Kinesis stream as a trigger
Validate Lambda function functionality
Configure DynamoDB setup
Conduct system testing by sending 100 records to Kinesis
Perform a DynamoDB scan operation
